etected_trace_keys\": [\"latency_spike\", \"checkoutservice->cartservice\", \"frontend->productcatalogservice\", \"...\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"延迟增幅非常显著，影响到多条调用链 (如 checkoutservice 和 frontend)\",\n      \"evidence\": \"在异常时段内，多个调用链显示延迟倍数显著上升\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n以上结果表明调用链中的延迟极可能集中发生在 `productcatalogservice` 服务中。这一点需要进一步的深入分析和性能调优，以避免影响整体服务质量。", "metric_analysis_findings": "异常指标数据已成功加载，现在将进入全面扫描以识别显著的异常调用链。\n\n### 数据提要\n分析时间范围为: **2025-06-27T10:10:33Z 至 2025-06-27T10:15:33Z**\n以下是显著变化的指标提取分析概要：\n\n#### 异常节点\n1. **Node 异常**\n   - `aiops-k8s-08`: `node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes`显著下降 (从 ~8.4GB 降至 ~5.8GB)\n   - `aiops-k8s-06`: `node_cpu_usage_rate`降低 (从 ~33.23 至 ~28.01)\n   - `aiops-k8s-04`: `node_memory_usage_rate`变化显著 (从 39.74% 至 32.89%)\n   \n异常节点主要是：`aiops-k8s-08`, 资源瓶颈特别突出。\n\n2. **显著影响 Pods**\n   根据 `node_pod_mapping`，`aiops-k8s-08` 上的 Pods 分别表现异常，主要关联以下指标和 Pods:\n   - **Pod:** `redis-cart-0`\n   - 异常指标包括 `pod_cpu_usage` 和 `pod_processes`\n\n3. 根因建议关键来源: 错误率未修正或Node资源瓶颈导致的性能负担。\n\nJSON格式返回分析结果:\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\",\n    \"node_cpu_usage_rate\",\n    \"pod_cpu_usage\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-08\",\n      \"reason\": \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes significantly dropped causing pods (redis-cart-0) degraded performance\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes decreased from 8.4GB to 5.8GB with a change ratio of 0.3657.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"pod_cpu_usage indicates that pod utilization became unstable, correlating with node degradation\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage change ratio was unusually high at 2.0 during the fault interval.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-06\",\n      \"reason\": \"node_cpu_usage_rate decreased by approximately 5% indicating CPU pressure redistribution.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_cpu_usage_rate fell from 33.23% to 28.01%, with a change ratio of 0.1705.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n这是全面扫描阶段的初步结果，其中聚焦于显著异常点以找出潜在影响的实体和指标，请评估关键组件对于之后深入诊断阶段的优先处理。"}
